public class SlideExpandableListAdapter
extends AbstractSlideExpandableListAdapter

ListAdapter that adds sliding functionality to a list. Uses R.id.expandalbe_toggle_button and R.id.expandable id's if no ids are given in the contructor.

Description copied from class: AbstractSlideExpandableListAdapter
This method is used to get the Button view that should expand or collapse the Expandable View.
Normally it will be implemented as: 
 return parent.findViewById(R.id.expand_toggle_button)
A listener will be attached to the button which will either expand or collapse the expandable view
